snippet.title: Mission Zero | Character Trailer: Gabriel
snippet.description:
Born in the underground city,「Gabriel」is now a powerful Mobius member owing countless money and absolute authority. Although he is rugged-looking, he is all things to all people. Everything is within his grasp. But who can imagine that such a domineering man can't sleep without his little unicorn doll?
------------------------------------
The Technical Test will start on July 8th. Please follow us to get first-hand information! 
- Pre-register now: https://www.missionzero.game/
- Discord: https://discord.gg/tQZTBYwgRC
- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Missionzerogame
